  status: ACTIVE
  scope: dev
  titre: Legacy Axial SCRIBE imported into V4
  l0_abstract: The previous Axial-Hybrid SCRIBE is preserved as V4 causal memory instead of being discarded during portable
    SCRIBE installation.
  l2_details: The old file was not valid V4 YAML as a whole, but its CAUSAL_CHAINING_YAML section and historical journal were
    parsed, deduplicated, normalized, and merged into this canonical SCRIBE.
  alternatives_rejetees:
  - nom: Discard legacy SCRIBE content
    raison_rejet: Would lose project scars, patterns, ghosts, and journals accumulated over 142 sessions.
  - nom: Keep only raw legacy file
    raison_rejet: Would preserve bytes but make retrieval/challenge unable to use historical memory.
