  hot_entries_consulted:
  - PAT-GRAPH-001
  - PAT-GIT-001
  l0_abstract: EOM and Volume Profile contract implemented.
  pourquoi: EOM was kept independent because its scaled price-volume unit belongs in a separate zero-baseline pane. Volume
    Profile was treated as a composite because POC, VAH, and VAL are inseparable outputs of one profile calculation; with
    daily OHLCV only, the UI must disclose approximation to avoid overstating market microstructure precision.
