  hot_entries_consulted:
  - PAT-GRAPH-001
  - PAT-EOM-VOLUME-PROFILE-COMPOSITE-CONTRACT-001
  l0_abstract: Pivot Points Standard and Fibonacci were separated into complete parent composites.
  pourquoi: The Fibonacci family needed its own parent and its own central pivot key because sharing the Standard pivot output
    made the UI semantically ambiguous. Both families now express the trader intent directly; activate the full system of
    horizontal levels, not isolated leaves.
  scribe_delta: PAT-PIVOT-POINTS-FAMILY-COMPOSITE-CONTRACT-001 | JOURNAL-002
  multi_agent_context:
    surface: technical-analysis-pivots
    other_agents_active: []
  titre: Pivot Points Standard/Fibonacci complete composite wiring.
- date: '2026-05-26'
  titre: VOLUME VARIATION KLINGER AND FORCE INDEX FULL WIRING
  llm: Codex GPT-5
  session_numero: 142
  taches_effectuees:
  - statut: DONE
    type: INDICATOR_WIRING
    description: Volume Oscillator, VROC14, Klinger Oscillator et Elder Force Index ne doivent plus rester backend-only; chaque
      activation traverse etat, persistance, worker, renderer, modal et Object Tree.
  - statut: DONE
    type: COMPOSITE_BOUNDARY
    description: Klinger est un parent composite fort avec Klinger Osc et Klinger Signal; Volume Oscillator et VROC14 restent
      des indicateurs atomiques en pourcentage.
  - statut: DONE
